title: Soundgarden, SXSW iTunes festival, 3:13 :2014.mp4
description: One of the most influential bands to emerge from the 90s seattle, Soundgarden introduced incendiary currents of heavy metal, Punk, and blues-rock muscle to the grunge revolution. The band celebrates the 20th anniversary of the watershed album"Super unknown" by performing it live in its entirety for the first time ever. Soundgarden performed at iTunes festival at SXSW (south by southwest)on March 13, 2014
